ack\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tdi1665703178578.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tdi1665703178578.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tdi1665703178578.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tdi1665703178578\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Builds a list of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Name=Value</var> pairs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__topic_d132551e1_d132552e1_d132553e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__p_d132554e1_d132555e1_d132556e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int PutItem(unsigned char *<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>, unsigned char *<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>, unsigned char *<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>, unsigned char **<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__section_w3799ab1b5b3_w3800ab1b5_w3801ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d737928e73\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__1\"> Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__2\"> Name </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__3\"> Direction </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__4\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__4\"> List to build </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__4\"> Name of item </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__4\"> Value of item </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char ** </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15794e1_d15795e1_d15796e1__entry__4\">Pointer to next location; <code class=\"ph codeph\">*next</code>\n                should be zero on the first call. The caller should not change the value. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__section_w3802ab1b5b5_w3803ab1b5_w3804ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d737928e190\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15797e1_d15798e1_d15799e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15797e1_d15798e1_d15799e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15797e1_d15798e1_d15799e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15797e1_d15798e1_d15799e1__entry__1\"> &gt;0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tdi1665703178578__table_d15797e1_d15798e1_d15799e1__entry__2\"> Length of list </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__section_w3805ab1b5b7_w3806ab1b5_w3807ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d737928e230\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__p_d132566e1_d132567e1_d132568e1\">This function builds a null-terminated list of items,\n        in which the items are separated by a byte value of 27, 0x1b. Items are pairs in the form\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">Name=Value</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__p_d132569e1_d132570e1_d132571e1\">Given the name and value, the function returns a\n        pointer to the next location to be used and the total length of the list. The function\n        inserts the separator if necessary.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__p_d132572e1_d132573e1_d132574e1\">The list names and values may be in UTF-8. Separators\n        such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> are in ASCII.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">In this example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">PutItem</code>  is being used to store the character set used: </p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104tdi1665703178578_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"tdi1665703178578__codeblock_s43_kp1_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/* Was Unicode or OEM negotiated ? */\n if (DrvArea-&gt;NegFlags &amp; FLG_NEGOTIATE_UNICODE)\n   PutItem(SecDrv-&gt;OutBuf, (USTRING*)\"CHARSET\", (USTRING*)\"UNICODE\", &amp;ptr);\n else\n   PutItem(SecDrv-&gt;OutBuf, (USTRING*)\"CHARSET\", (USTRING*)\"OEM\", &amp;ptr);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532295\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532295\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PutItem Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Builds a list of Name=Value pairs. int PutItem(unsigned char * List , unsigned char * Name , unsigned char * Value , unsigned char ** Next ) Parameters Type Name Direction Description unsigned char * List IN List to build unsigned char * Name IN Name of item unsigned char * Value IN Value of item unsigned char ** Next OUT Pointer to next location; *next should be zero on the first call. The caller should not change the value. Return Values Value Description >0 Length of list Description This function builds a null-terminated list of items, in which the items are separated by a byte value of 27, 0x1b. Items are pairs in the form Name=Value . Given the name and value, the function returns a pointer to the next location to be used and the total length of the list. The function inserts the separator if necessary. The list names and values may be in UTF-8. Separators such as = are in ASCII. In this example, PutItem is being used to store the character set used: Explain this code /* Was Unicode or OEM negotiated ? */ if (DrvArea->NegFlags & FLG_NEGOTIATE_UNICODE) PutItem(SecDrv->OutBuf, (USTRING*)\"CHARSET\", (USTRING*)\"UNICODE\", &ptr); else PutItem(SecDrv->OutBuf, (USTRING*)\"CHARSET\", (USTRING*)\"OEM\", &ptr); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}